    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>How I love the photos of empty cups &#8211; adorable. As I usually find hot chocolate too sweet for my tastes, I often add a shot of (now-decaf) espresso to my cup, sometimes with a bit of cinnamon as well. This recipe looks indulgent and lovely, exactly what it should be! All the best to you and Brandon on your upcoming classes!</p>
