    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>The best thing about making hot chocolate with real chocolate and in a blender is that people who easily burn their tongues can wait for it to cool a bit without all the cocoa powder falling to the bottom.  </></>I was gifted a blender this Christmas by my soon-to-be mother-in-law (this I used enough hyphens there?) so I will definitely be trying out this recipe soon.</p>
