    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I like that your hot chocolate recipe is on the lighter side. We all need a break from the heavy winter celebrating&#8230;</></>But, speaking of heavy foods &#038; celebrating, I couldn&#8217;t help but notice the Galette du Rois on Dorie Greenspan&#8217;s site&#8230; any plans for concocting one of your own??</></>Lastly, I felt a bit proud as I read the combined Husband&#038;Wife bio for the cooking class you&#8217;ll be teaching. Congrats on this an other the other wonderful accomplishments you&#8217;ve managed over the past year! ðŸ™‚</p>
