    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Your description of such a comfort (and the pictures of those empty glasses, with just enough hot chocolate clinging to the inside of the mug to allow me to imagine what had been in there before) made me want to run the store and buy some chocolate right this very second.  </></>And a P.S. &#8211; I just read your column in Bon Appetit &#8211; it is beautiful (though I must say I expected nothing less)</p>
