    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;m sipping this for breakfast as I sit and type this.  It&#8217;s perfect.  I also second Beth&#8217;s cheers and gratitude for &#8220;successfully, soulfully and stylishly steering your lives toward the things you love.&#8221;  It&#8217;s pretty wonderful, this life you&#8217;ve made for yourself.  I hope you sometimes do wiggly little victory dances in your kitchen.</p>
