      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/01/from-this-day-forth/#comment-9316"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-01-09T20:12:00-05:00">Wednesday, January 9, 2008 at 8:12 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>funny, i think the last time i had hot chocolate was also in paris, almost ten years ago!  but i had the thickest of thick varieties &#8212; i probably could have eaten it with a fork. ðŸ™‚  somehow i can&#8217;t get as excited about hot chocolate in the US &#8212; plus, somehow the calories never bothered me in France, but I will admit I get a little frightened of Starbuck&#8217;s 4-ounce 600-calorie chocolate drinks.  obviously the solution is to make my own the next time i&#8217;m craving it!  great recipe.</p>
