      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/01/from-this-day-forth/#comment-9325"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-01-10T21:46:00-05:00">Thursday, January 10, 2008 at 9:46 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I am new to your blog and loving the recipes and photos!  I&#8217;m a chocoholic so will be trying the hot chocolate recipe tonight.  I also want to try the brussel sprout/pine nut/ pasta recipe &#8211; can I substitute the heavy cream with something lower in fat?  Thanks.</p>
