      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/01/from-this-day-forth/#comment-9326"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-01-10T22:05:00-05:00">Thursday, January 10, 2008 at 10:05 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly,</></>First, congrats on Bon App &#8211; I am so impressed; you must be so proud, (in your own special, humble way).  </></>So about this hot chocolate &#8211; I am wondering what the little bit of water adds?  Could I skip it or is there some sort of chemistry occuring with the chocolate and frothing? </></>Thanks!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-9326' data-commentid="9326" data-postid="1337" data-belowelement="comment-9326" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Kirsten" aria-label='Reply to Kirsten'>Reply</a>    </div>
