    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>decade diary, I&#39;ve never tried this recipe with cocoa, but I have a feeling that it would be very, very different.  The chocolate is what gives this recipe its richness and body, and without it, I think you&#39;ll just have standard hot cocoa.  I think I&#39;d wait until I had some chocolate on hand, if I were you.  Happy weekend!</p>
